The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect clickbait articles. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves text classification and information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of neural networks and attention mechanisms suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of embeddings, which is a common technique in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
